title: PSP - Gran Turismo - UMDRip (NTSC)
description:
Gran Turismo game in full .ISO format. NTSC (America) format. This file is not compressed. If you would like to compress it, look up PSP Compressor on CNET (download.com) and you will find a free program that compresses it into a .CSO format. 

To play this, you need a modded PSP. If you don't have mod, this will NOT work.

To install onto Memory Stick, connect your PSP to your PC, enable USB mode, and copy this file into a folder called "ISO" (no quotation marks) in the root of your card. If it doesn't work correctly, let me know in a comment and I'll try to re-up it.
